{"tid":590302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵東鐵線列車遭塗鴉　疑未趕及清洗　今晨驚現列車一度載客","createTime":"2018-03-12T13:27:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T13:37:23.000Z","uid":1735,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"68239e00deca50ab5c4e080e6b47568a791a0b4d","tid":590302,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T13:27:31.000Z","msg":"港鐵發言人表示，今晨約7時15分，港鐵職員於羅湖往紅磡方向的月台發現，涉事列車的車尾左邊車身有塗鴉。由於塗鴉不影響列車安全，為減低對乘客影響，列車一直開至沙田，才請乘客下車，轉乘另一班車。涉事列車其後駛往旺角東備用月台，以便之後駛回車廠清潔。港鐵表示，已報警求助，警方將事件列為刑事毀壞案處理。港鐵又呼籲市民，破壞公物，包括塗鴉，都是刑事罪行，市民不要以身試法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/212653_076a60d3928b007521046df774d20608.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F212653_076a60d3928b007521046df774d20608.png&h=69bc2b84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於今次東鐵線列車遭塗鴉，大批網民均大讚「好靚」，創意藝術，更要求港鐵不要清洗走。<br />\n<br />\n美國情侶成港鐵塗鴉「常客」<br />\n<br />\n事實上，這並非港鐵列車首次被塗鴉。翻查資料，一對來自美國的情侶UTAH 及ETHER，於2011至2015年間，曾至少3次闖入港鐵車廠及車站。2011年7月7日晚上，柴灣車廠保安就發現一列車車身有塗鴉；之後2012年及2015年時，都曾發現塗鴉列車事件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/212712_a7be35e0017808fa28aea54464e111ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F212712_a7be35e0017808fa28aea54464e111ca.png&h=18ea4b44&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/212713_0cd39d64e008f96ce2617737856cfe80.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F212713_0cd39d64e008f96ce2617737856cfe80.png&h=fea6fd8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，去年1月網上流傳一張相片，相中所見，港鐵上水站的月台車站牌背後的不銹鋼，被人用白色顏料，模仿上水站內的指示牌字體，臨摹出「上水」兩字。<br />\n<br />\nSource: hk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 1"},{"pid":"40844de3a55f62cf55a15078af330d69562619dd","tid":590302,"uid":37240,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T13:28:22.000Z","msg":"靚好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65a785c05dd28b7bba8ff0fcdb62927b251bf29","tid":590302,"uid":18764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68239e00deca50ab5c4e080e6b47568a791a0b4d","tid":590302,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T13:27:31.000Z","msg":"港鐵發言人表示，今晨約7時15分，港鐵職員於羅湖往紅磡方向的月台發現，涉事列車的車尾左邊車身有塗鴉。由於塗鴉不影響列車安全，為減低對乘客影響，列車一直開至沙田，才請乘客下車，轉乘另一班車。涉事列車其後駛往旺角東備用月台，以便之後駛回車廠清潔。港鐵表示，已報警求助，警方將事件列為刑事毀壞案處理。港鐵又呼籲市民，破壞公物，包括塗鴉，都是刑事罪行，市民不要以身試法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/212653_076a60d3928b007521046df774d20608.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F212653_076a60d3928b007521046df774d20608.png&h=69bc2b84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於今次東鐵線列車遭塗鴉，大批網民均大讚「好靚」，創意藝術，更要求港鐵不要清洗走。<br />\n<br />\n美國情侶成港鐵塗鴉「常客」<br />\n<br />\n事實上，這並非港鐵列車首次被塗鴉。翻查資料，一對來自美國的情侶UTAH 及ETHER，於2011至2015年間，曾至少3次闖入港鐵車廠及車站。2011年7月7日晚上，柴灣車廠保安就發現一列車車身有塗鴉；之後2012年及2015年時，都曾發現塗鴉列車事件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/212712_a7be35e0017808fa28aea54464e111ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F212712_a7be35e0017808fa28aea54464e111ca.png&h=18ea4b44&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/212713_0cd39d64e008f96ce2617737856cfe80.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F212713_0cd39d64e008f96ce2617737856cfe80.png&h=fea6fd8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，去年1月網上流傳一張相片，相中所見，港鐵上水站的月台車站牌背後的不銹鋼，被人用白色顏料，模仿上水站內的指示牌字體，臨摹出「上水」兩字。<br />\n<br />\nSource: hk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 1"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T13:28:29.000Z","msg":"幾靚"},{"pid":"783ff99077909b177a9a60310e6bbec5ced8227e","tid":590302,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T13:29:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d2ecbc3068394f72679217f0eed4a4ad76e07d","tid":590302,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T13:29:37.000Z","msg":"靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8e2cd887de921a5bca21b37b1a4587c283d8e6","tid":590302,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T13:31:04.000Z","msg":"真係幾型"},{"pid":"8f82f7ac48e5dcfd41285cf9bc7a750a925239de","tid":590302,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T13:33:53.000Z","msg":"無諗過可以咁靚"},{"pid":"ee63c7e3775d72b7961880641f4300fb15a3f2c5","tid":590302,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T13:35:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed109e0c56af950c6fa2cac7668f4f92d740b422","tid":590302,"uid":73575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T13:37:23.000Z","msg":"比著係支那人畫就冇人話靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}